<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>59</hymn_number>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tuhin Lalpa ka hun mui,
 Min dang him sam puong ka;
 Nangmah angsung ah cheng ingka,
 Hehpihna tuisuohgiet ah.

[V2]
 Ka Lal na hi, hun mung ka ie,
 Hun mung ka ie, Ka Lal na hi;
 Aw nei hehpih zie ka hetin,
 Na thuok ie Kalvari-ah.

[V3]
 2. Aw na thawkna Kalvari,
 Thil ingka khawvelah;
 Hehpihna ziekin hun mung ka,
 Aw, Na vakzawi ni sang in.

[V4]
 3. Mipi leh Lal lopite'n,
 Musit in kimvel ui;
 Nang vang gimtheite Lalpa mai,
 Kei di'n Na huntai Lalpa.

[V5]
 4. Na pienna lei mundawng pen,
 Na thihna Kalvari;
 Na gimtheihna kei le chang ka,
 Nuom hun sangka Nang vang in.</lyrics>
<title>Ka Lal Na Hi</title>
</song>